These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-1::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, skateboarding, skiing
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is not to the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##8
3. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |    3     |
| Sport   | skiing | skateboarding | lacrosse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: reading, fishing, woodworking
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is not to the left of the person who's hobby is reading##8
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3     |
| Hobby   | reading | woodworking | fishing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, almond-milk, cola
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person drinking coffee is not to the right of the person drinking cola##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |  3  |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | coffee | cola |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-4::.
